&lt;p&gt;&lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;Reporting into the&amp;nbsp;Enterprise Application&amp;nbsp;function, this individual will&amp;nbsp;be responsible for&amp;nbsp;day-to-day NetSuite administration, system optimization, and cross-functional initiatives that improve how we quote, sell, bill, and recognize revenue. This role will also partner closely with Salesforce stakeholders to ensure seamless data flow across the revenue stack.&lt;/span&gt; &lt;span data-contrast=&quot;auto&quot;&gt;This is a hands-on role for someone who thrives in a fast-moving environment and wants to build systems that directly power business outcomes.&lt;/span&gt;&lt;span data-ccp-props=&quot;{&amp;quot;134233117&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;134233118&amp;quot;:true,&amp;quot;201341983&amp;quot;:0,&amp;quot;335559740&amp;quot;:240}&quot;&gt;&amp;nbsp;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
